2026-05-16T19:17:44.3236453Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3237099Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3237769Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3238711Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3239433Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3240140Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T19:17:44.3240777Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
